@startuml seq_28_handle_global_reports
title Sequence Diagram: UC-28 Handle Global Reports

actor Admin
participant "Admin Web" as Frontend
participant "Admin Report Controller" as Controller
participant "Report Service" as Service
participant "Report Repo" as Repo

Admin -> Frontend: Open Global Reports Dashboard
Frontend -> Controller: GET /api/admin/reports?filter=...
Controller -> Service: Get Reports
Service -> Repo: Validate Admin Access
Repo --> Service: Access valid
Service -> Repo: Fetch filtered reports
Repo --> Service: List of Reports
Service --> Controller: Reports Data
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> Admin: Display reports table

Admin -> Frontend: Select report(s) & Click Delete
Frontend -> Controller: DELETE /api/admin/reports {report_ids}
Controller -> Service: Delete Reports
Service -> Repo: Validate Admin Access
Repo --> Service: Access valid
Service -> Repo: Soft/Hard delete selected report records
Repo --> Service: Reports deleted
Service --> Controller: Success
Controller --> Frontend: 200 OK
Frontend --> Admin: Remove reports from dashboard UI
@enduml